  "text": "Here we use another algorithm developed by McKay [CITATION_1] , called canonical augmentation. The ingredients for this are a question like the one we are considering, a canonical labeling function as described, a way of computing the automorphism group of a code, and a hereditary structure on the objects to be generated.",
